  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 14th level, on a long rest select a second Puppet Weapon Type for your Puppet Tool.</p><p> Your Puppet Tool, as part of commanding it can transform into or out of this second Weapon Type, gaining all its benefits.</p><p> As an object interaction, you can reduce the current and maximum hit points of your Puppet Tool by 1/3rd to utilize its Weapon Mode and normal Puppet form at the same time (You do not count as your Puppet Tool while using the Weapon Mode this way).</p><p> Reverting this effect takes a Bonus Action, giving the Puppet back its hp.</p><p> Finally, at the start of combat or as a Bonus Action, you can swap one Tactic from your Tactics of the Craft feature.</p><p></p>",
